{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/Steam_Storefront_Banner_Graphic_-_1.png?t=1729611467\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a twist of fate, our heroes learn of a safe haven ark. Their journey ends at its gates, only to be shunned\u2014King Chipmunk has reserved every spot on the upper deck! What a jerk. Amidst a crowd of seatless creatures, there\u2019s but one option left: dethrone the tyrant chipmunk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/Steam_Storefront_Banner_Graphic_-_2.png?t=1729611467\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/CC_GIF5.gif?t=1729611467\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play at your own pace through async multiplayer! Chill out in Arena Mode and battle against user-generated teams to earn 10 Victories. Want to test your skills? Climb the leaderboard in Rapture Mode and utilize powerful Buff Cards to build an overpowered squad while battling endless waves of teams.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/Steam_Storefront_Banner_Graphic_-_3.png?t=1729611467\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2377230/extras/CC_GIF1.gif?t=1729611467\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The flood is coming. Only the Ark will save them. That is\u2026 unless the evil King Chipmunk reserves all the seats! Fight for your own salvation and hone your skills in a complete single-player campaign filled with hand-drawn cutscenes and art. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img cla